      <p id="Par15">In new t-test definitions and in Eqs. (S27) and (S38) in <xref rid="MOESM1" ref-type="media">Supplementary Statistical Methods</xref>, <inline-formula id="IEq137"><alternatives><tex-math id="M281">\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
