      <p id="Par31">We also simulated FACS data of CRISPR knockout screen to compare NBBt-test, edgeR, DESeq2, Baggerly, and MAGeCK in 8 scenarios (see <xref rid="Sec16" ref-type="sec">Methods</xref> section). Likewise, NBBt-test still had much better performance than the other four methods in all these 8 scenarios (Supplementary Fig. <xref rid="MOESM2" ref-type="media">S5</xref>). Except for scenarios g and h, NBBt-test had the highest F1-score across − log10(<inline-formula id="IEq195"><alternatives><tex-math id="M417">\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
